# Upstash Redis — required in production (Vercel). Without these the app
# falls back to an in-memory store, which only works in local `next dev`
# (a single process) and will NOT sync across serverless instances.
#
# Create a free database at https://console.upstash.com/ → Redis,
# then copy the "REST API" URL + token here (and into Vercel project env vars).
UPSTASH_REDIS_REST_URL=
UPSTASH_REDIS_REST_TOKEN=
